  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, the Jewish children were excluded from the two non-denominational-- because I would call the lyceum was also more-- less-- it wasn't so religiously influenced like the Catholic monastery school.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were allowed in a class of 30, one Jewish child.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now my brother, my cousins-- one of my cousins who later became an eminent professor in philosophy studied in Oxford and was a professor at Tel Aviv University-- all came-- all went to that school, even my parent-- my father and his brothers as well, so my family was desperate to get me into that school.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But again, it's anti-Jewish regulation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was practically impossible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was no appeal against it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The schools got their instructions from the Minister of Education and they acted upon.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The story goes on there that I have been kept at home by my parents, which was against the law, for a month, in the month of September 1940, until representations were made by my uncle, the lawyer, and my father went to Budapest to see the parliamentary representative of Sopron, who happened to be Count Csaky, who was the foreign minister.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And because of the family's connection, the intervention I think was the sole and only case which I have ever heard of where the foreign ministry gave instructions to the Minister of Education to instruct the Szechenyi Istvan gymnasium to admit me, which they did in October, 1940.",
      "word_count": 48
    }
  ],
